                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Dawson</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-09-30">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 30, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Dawson reports that the Dominican Government refuses to recognize the award
                    unless 60 per cent of the custom receipts are reserved for administrative
                    expenditures.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
